{
  "_tutorial_zh": [
    "\u003d\u003d\u003d 武器脚本效果配置 \u003d\u003d\u003d",
    "定义武器的特殊效果",
    "",
    "事件类型：",
    "  onHit: 攻击命中时",
    "  onKill: 击杀时",
    "  onHurt: 被攻击时",
    "  whenHeld: 主手持有时 (每5tick)",
    "",
    "变量：",
    "  self: 武器持有者",
    "  victim: 目标 (onHit/onKill) 或攻击者 (onHurt)",
    "",
    "示例动作：",
    "  victim.setFire(3) - 点燃3秒",
    "  victim.addPotion(\u0027poison\u0027, 100, 1) - 中毒",
    "  self.heal(2) - 恢复2血"
  ],
  "_tutorial_en": [
    "\u003d\u003d\u003d Weapon Script Effects Config \u003d\u003d\u003d",
    "Defines special weapon effects",
    "",
    "Event types:",
    "  onHit: On attack hit",
    "  onKill: On kill",
    "  onHurt: When hurt",
    "  whenHeld: While held (every 5 ticks)",
    "",
    "Variables:",
    "  self: Weapon holder",
    "  victim: Target (onHit/onKill) or attacker (onHurt)",
    "",
    "Example actions:",
    "  victim.setFire(3) - Ignite 3s",
    "  victim.addPotion(\u0027poison\u0027, 100, 1) - Poison",
    "  self.heal(2) - Heal 2"
  ],
  "_example": {
    "_comment": "复制到 scripts 数组使用 / Copy to scripts array to use",
    "id": "emeralddagger",
    "events": [
      {
        "event": "onHit",
        "actions": [
          "victim.addPotion(\u0027glowing\u0027, 60, 0)"
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
